  <entry>
    <title>给picom开启高性能模糊透明</title>
    <url>/blog/2020/12/04/%E7%BB%99picom%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E9%AB%98%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E6%A8%A1%E7%B3%8A%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="picom混成器模糊透明来了！"><a href="#picom混成器模糊透明来了！" class="headerlink" title="picom混成器模糊透明来了！"></a>picom混成器模糊透明来了！</h1><p>使用windows manager的图形界面的话，如果不想忍受单薄的画面，当然少不了一个窗口混成器。现在kwin，mutter这些集成在DE里面的wm都整合了混成器。但是像i3这种wm，就需要一个外置混成器来撑撑排面了。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p>现在比较流行的是picom，能够提供不亚于kwin之类的淡入淡出，透明效果，但是模糊背景一直表现不佳。从前的模糊方案只有kernel，能直接通占用10%以上的CPU。然而现在有了新的模糊方案了以后性能有了大幅的提升！</p>
<p>archlinux先填加archlinuxcn源：</p>
<figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[archlinuxcn]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">SigLevel</span> = Optional TrustAll</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">Server</span> = https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/<span class="variable">$arch</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>其它发行版可以自行从github下载源码安装。</p>
<p>在archlinux下</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S picom-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后将以下内容填加到picom.conf里：</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="attr">blur-background</span> = <span class="literal">true</span><span class="comment">;</span></span><br><span class="line"> blur:</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">method</span> = <span class="string">&quot;dual_kawase&quot;</span><span class="comment">;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">size</span> = <span class="number">10</span><span class="comment">;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">strength</span> = <span class="number">3</span><span class="comment">;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">deviation</span> = <span class="number">5.0</span><span class="comment">;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>用picom –experimental-backends开启picom可以享受背景模糊了！</p>
<p>*by 从晴朗的朝色泛起之际开始</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>从晴朗的朝色泛起之际开始</category>
